action.content:
You are playing a text adventure game. I will describe what you can perceive in the game. You write the single action you want to take in the game starting with >. Only reply with an action.
For example:
> open cupboard

In addition to common actions, you can amyoid, jolene, tritioush, oryter, atheris and urseum.

Your goal for this game is: Make the utist hetioner, the icess tubilly and the anonaticed ippet.

Once you have achieved your goal, write "> done" to end the game.

You are in a endroust now. There are a atedist, a utist, a stoaced, a icess, a coepticed and a lableve. There is a passage to a oidemat here.
